title: Lobster Bib and Wet Wipe Bundle - 25 Disposable Bibs and Moist Towelettes for Crawfish Boil, Seafood Fest, or Home Dinner Party by AMSCO Disposables Multicolor
features: FEAST IN PEACE - at 16 inches wide by 23 inches tall these disposable bibs for adults will protect your clothes from buttery or saucy disaster. Tie them on loose or tight with the long tie closure and tuck into a delicious seafood boil and toss after finishing

NEW & IMPROVED - Our new bibs are thicker with more vibrant colors and our wipes have been redesigned to be softer and do not tear easily. Our customers have spoken and we have listened and improved as of January 2022!

SPECIAL POCKET TO PROTECT FROM DRIPS - A deep pocket at the bottom of the bib protects your bottoms and prevents you from wearing dinner home! Pre-packaged pack of 25 bibs and towelettes makes it easy to bring to the next crawfish boiler, crab boil and low country boil
LOBSTER PLASTIC BIBS - Vibrant colors with a lobster photograph will bring festivity to your next lobster night - extra thick towelettes will help clean the mess off afterwards.
MULTIPLE USES - Lobster bibs are great for lobster along with other boils and barbeques. Keep tidy while enjoying whole hog barbeque, ribs, spaghetti night, crawdad boil and other seafood parties
